It is a well established, that irradiation by any particle introduces effectively negative space charge in detectors processed on float zone silicon, which is most commonly used. The change in effective doping concentration is reflected in the full depletion voltage Vfd, needed to establish the electric field in the entire detector: 21.30Vfd=e0|Neff|W22𝜖0𝜖.\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
